  "prompt": "How I make a call in Jio sim?",
  "response": "To make a call using a Jio SIM, follow these steps:\n\n1. Ensure your phone is charged and has a good signal.\n\n2. Open the Phone or Dialer app on your smartphone.\n\n3. Using the keypad, enter the phone number you want to call:\n- For local numbers: Dial the 10-digit mobile number\n- For landline numbers: Dial the area code + phone number\n- For international numbers: Dial +, country code, and phone number\n\n4. Press the green call button or call icon to initiate the call.\n\n5. If you want to call from your contacts:\n- Open Contacts app\n- Select the contact you want to call\n- Tap on the phone number to call\n\nAdditional tips:\n- Ensure you have sufficient balance or active plan\n- Check network coverage\n- For international calls, verify international calling rates\n- If facing issues, contact Jio customer care at 198\n\nNote: The exact steps might slightly vary depending on your specific phone model and operating system (Android or iOS).",
